00:00:14.949 --> 00:00:18.786 position:7% line:83% align:start
[SHINOZAKI] I work for a Santa
who's so small and cute.

00:00:18.920 --> 00:00:21.823 position:13% line:83% align:start
We've got a lot of presents
to deliver this year!

00:00:21.956 --> 00:00:24.324 position:7% line:89% align:start
Let's do our best for the kids!

00:00:24.458 --> 00:00:25.392 position:41% line:89% align:start
Right!

00:00:25.527 --> 00:00:27.695 position:35% line:83% align:start
Here we go.
We're almost there.

00:00:27.829 --> 00:00:29.631 position:21% line:83% align:start
-Just a little more.
[SHINOZAKI] -It's as big as her.

00:00:29.764 --> 00:00:31.198 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hmmm!

00:00:31.331 --> 00:00:32.634 position:35% line:83% align:start
[SHINOZAKI]
Hey, Santa?

00:00:32.767 --> 00:00:35.135 position:19% line:89% align:start
Mind sharing that joy?

00:00:35.670 --> 00:00:37.070 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:00:38.573 --> 00:00:41.108 position:19% line:83% align:start
What's gotten into you
all of a sudden?

00:00:41.241 --> 00:00:42.577 position:30% line:89% align:start
Silly reindeer!

00:00:42.710 --> 00:00:45.112 position:30% line:83% align:start
I know today is
our busiest day of the year,

00:00:45.245 --> 00:00:47.347 position:7% line:83% align:start
but let's try not to overdo it,
okay?

00:00:47.481 --> 00:00:50.217 position:30% line:83% align:start
Can't share joy
if you don't have enough energy.

00:00:51.619 --> 00:00:53.888 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Santa?
-Yes, what?

00:00:54.022 --> 00:00:57.825 position:7% line:83% align:start
While I do appreciate the hug,
I wasn't asking for one.

00:00:57.959 --> 00:01:00.562 position:19% line:83% align:start
I was offering to carry
some of the presents.

00:01:02.997 --> 00:01:04.264 position:44% line:89% align:start
Aaah!

00:01:04.398 --> 00:01:06.734 position:10% line:89% align:start
Oh no, I'm so sorry for that!

00:01:06.868 --> 00:01:07.936 position:30% line:89% align:start
No, it's fine.

00:01:08.068 --> 00:01:09.971 position:38% line:83% align:start
It was a
simple misunderstanding!

00:01:10.505 --> 00:01:13.775 position:13% line:83% align:start
[SHINOZAKI] Mistake or not,
I just got a hug from Santa!

00:01:14.441 --> 00:01:16.376 position:38% line:83% align:start
[SHIORI]
I'm so embarrassed,

00:01:16.511 --> 00:01:19.681 position:21% line:83% align:start
but he said it's fine
and it's Christmas.

00:01:19.814 --> 00:01:21.049 position:33% line:89% align:start
Are you okay?

00:01:21.181 --> 00:01:22.984 position:16% line:83% align:start
Yes, just thinking about
yuletide cheer!

00:01:23.116 --> 00:01:24.652 position:38% line:89% align:start
[laughs]

00:01:24.786 --> 00:01:27.522 position:19% line:83% align:start
A very Merry Christmas,
one and all!

00:01:28.923 --> 00:01:30.123 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:01:30.959 --> 00:01:32.760 position:30% line:89% align:start
What was that?

00:01:32.894 --> 00:01:34.729 position:38% line:83% align:start
-[chimes]
-Huh?

00:01:35.462 --> 00:01:37.832 position:41% line:83% align:start
[AKINA]
Dreams can be weird, huh?

00:01:38.633 --> 00:01:40.802 position:35% line:83% align:start
[SHINOZAKI]
How does he know about it?

00:03:13.460 --> 00:03:16.998 position:30% line:83% align:start
[AKINA] Oh, my!
This is quite the turnout!

00:03:17.131 --> 00:03:18.633 position:35% line:89% align:start
I'm sorry.

00:03:18.766 --> 00:03:21.035 position:7% line:83% align:start
You probably have better things
you could be doing today.

00:03:21.169 --> 00:03:22.136 position:33% line:89% align:start
Not a thing!

00:03:22.269 --> 00:03:23.638 position:7% line:89% align:start
So, why not help out a friend?

00:03:23.771 --> 00:03:26.641 position:19% line:83% align:start
Besides, I helped draw
your doujinshi.

00:03:26.774 --> 00:03:28.442 position:7% line:89% align:start
Of course I'd help you sell it.

00:03:28.576 --> 00:03:30.410 position:7% line:89% align:start
Well, I can't argue with that.

00:03:30.545 --> 00:03:33.047 position:13% line:89% align:start
Hmm! I wish I could though.

00:03:33.181 --> 00:03:35.449 position:38% line:89% align:start
[snoring]

00:03:35.583 --> 00:03:38.619 position:21% line:83% align:start
I know what that sigh
means. Manga pains?

00:03:38.753 --> 00:03:40.454 position:13% line:89% align:start
The deadline's in two days.

00:03:40.588 --> 00:03:42.023 position:16% line:89% align:start
I asked my artist friends

00:03:42.156 --> 00:03:44.491 position:24% line:83% align:start
if they could help,
but they were all too busy.

00:03:44.625 --> 00:03:47.028 position:10% line:89% align:start
I'm sorry. That sounds rough.

00:03:47.161 --> 00:03:48.763 position:41% line:83% align:start
[AKINA]
Rough, you say?

00:03:48.896 --> 00:03:50.565 position:27% line:89% align:start
Oh, dear. How so?

00:03:50.698 --> 00:03:52.299 position:16% line:89% align:start
It's really not that bad!

00:03:52.432 --> 00:03:53.968 position:35% line:89% align:start
[laughing]

00:03:54.102 --> 00:03:56.369 position:38% line:89% align:start
[screams]

00:03:56.504 --> 00:03:58.371 position:7% line:89% align:start
It's an outside of work thingy.

00:03:58.506 --> 00:04:00.875 position:21% line:83% align:start
I'm happy to help in
any way I can!

00:04:01.809 --> 00:04:03.343 position:13% line:89% align:start
Thank you, but I'm not sure

00:04:03.477 --> 00:04:05.513 position:21% line:83% align:start
how qualified you are
to help me.

00:04:05.646 --> 00:04:07.247 position:38% line:83% align:start
[SHIORI]
You'd be surprised.

00:04:07.380 --> 00:04:09.416 position:19% line:83% align:start
He was qualified enough
to draw this

00:04:09.550 --> 00:04:11.819 position:21% line:83% align:start
in-store installation
template for us.

00:04:11.953 --> 00:04:13.154 position:41% line:89% align:start
No way?

00:04:13.286 --> 00:04:14.856 position:13% line:89% align:start
Are you on a new game plus?

00:04:14.989 --> 00:04:16.858 position:21% line:89% align:start
I don't believe I am.

00:04:19.227 --> 00:04:21.162 position:16% line:89% align:start
Okay. Are you hearing me?

00:04:21.294 --> 00:04:22.964 position:19% line:89% align:start
Loud and clear, ma'am!

00:04:23.097 --> 00:04:26.134 position:13% line:83% align:start
And did you get the link to
the cloud folder I sent to you?

00:04:26.266 --> 00:04:27.168 position:35% line:89% align:start
I sure did!

00:04:27.300 --> 00:04:28.870 position:35% line:89% align:start
All right.

00:04:29.003 --> 00:04:31.205 position:7% line:83% align:start
Could you please work on pages
sixteen through twenty-two?

00:04:31.338 --> 00:04:35.342 position:7% line:83% align:start
I sure can! And could you check
my work as I finish each page?

00:04:35.475 --> 00:04:37.011 position:24% line:89% align:start
Yeah, that's fine.

00:04:37.145 --> 00:04:39.147 position:16% line:83% align:start
[HAYAKAWA] I wasn't sure
about working with a normie

00:04:39.279 --> 00:04:40.648 position:16% line:89% align:start
on an eighteen-plus book,

00:04:40.782 --> 00:04:43.450 position:5% line:83% align:start
but if I do all the spicy scenes
it should be fine.

00:04:44.218 --> 00:04:47.555 position:19% line:83% align:start
[AKINA] I have to say,
I'm very impressed, Hayakawa.

00:04:47.688 --> 00:04:48.388 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:04:48.523 --> 00:04:49.991 position:24% line:89% align:start
This is incredible!

00:04:50.124 --> 00:04:52.292 position:10% line:83% align:start
And to think you made it all
from scratch.

00:04:52.425 --> 00:04:55.530 position:21% line:83% align:start
Hmm! It's kind of you
to say that.

00:04:56.764 --> 00:04:59.167 position:7% line:83% align:start
[HAYAKAWA] But considering this
is a BL doujinshi

00:04:59.299 --> 00:05:00.568 position:5% line:89% align:start
of an already existing property,

00:05:00.701 --> 00:05:02.770 position:24% line:83% align:start
I wouldn't call it
"from scratch".

00:05:02.904 --> 00:05:06.507 position:7% line:83% align:start
I just finished my first page!
Tell me what you think!

00:05:06.641 --> 00:05:08.810 position:30% line:89% align:start
Wow, he's fast.

00:05:09.309 --> 00:05:11.411 position:35% line:89% align:start
Nice work!

00:05:11.546 --> 00:05:13.181 position:7% line:89% align:start
Except you should have told me

00:05:13.313 --> 00:05:16.884 position:19% line:83% align:start
I accidentally gave you
a spicy scene to work on!

00:05:18.219 --> 00:05:19.520 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hmm!

00:05:19.654 --> 00:05:21.589 position:30% line:83% align:start
You know what,
this has been a lot of fun!

00:05:21.722 --> 00:05:23.791 position:30% line:83% align:start
Our first joint
creative project.

00:05:23.925 --> 00:05:26.727 position:16% line:83% align:start
And now there's a new hot
and heavy BL in the world.

00:05:26.861 --> 00:05:28.596 position:10% line:89% align:start
It's the product of our love!

00:05:28.729 --> 00:05:30.031 position:21% line:89% align:start
For my sanity's sake,

00:05:30.164 --> 00:05:32.233 position:10% line:83% align:start
please stop talking about it
like it's a baby!

00:05:32.733 --> 00:05:35.570 position:7% line:83% align:start
Here's hoping our love product
will sell like hotcakes!

00:05:35.703 --> 00:05:36.971 position:16% line:89% align:start
Now I'm starting to think

00:05:37.104 --> 00:05:39.240 position:27% line:83% align:start
that sounds like
a more fitting title for it.

00:05:39.372 --> 00:05:40.575 position:35% line:89% align:start
[chuckles]

00:05:40.708 --> 00:05:42.409 position:38% line:83% align:start
[HARUNA]
Is that Chika, IRL?

00:05:42.977 --> 00:05:46.214 position:19% line:83% align:start
Hey, how have you been?
I haven't seen you in forever.

00:05:46.346 --> 00:05:49.951 position:13% line:83% align:start
Hey Haruna! I've been doing
pretty good since last summer.

00:05:50.585 --> 00:05:52.153 position:30% line:89% align:start
So, I can see.

00:05:52.286 --> 00:05:54.055 position:30% line:89% align:start
How do you do?

00:05:54.188 --> 00:05:56.057 position:35% line:83% align:start
-Boyfriend!
-What? No!

00:05:56.190 --> 00:05:57.490 position:30% line:89% align:start
He's from work!

00:05:57.625 --> 00:05:59.293 position:16% line:83% align:start
I told you I needed help
finishing my doujinshi

00:05:59.426 --> 00:06:00.862 position:24% line:89% align:start
and he stepped up!

00:06:00.995 --> 00:06:04.332 position:19% line:83% align:start
Oh! You guys must work
well together then. Really well.

00:06:04.464 --> 00:06:06.167 position:10% line:89% align:start
Why do you say it like that?

00:06:06.300 --> 00:06:07.635 position:33% line:89% align:start
What's this?

00:06:07.768 --> 00:06:09.770 position:30% line:83% align:start
Excuse me miss,
but is that charm Hime-chan

00:06:09.904 --> 00:06:11.572 position:10% line:89% align:start
from the Kimihime-chan anime?

00:06:11.706 --> 00:06:14.342 position:27% line:83% align:start
A man of culture?
How did you get into it?

00:06:14.474 --> 00:06:17.979 position:5% line:83% align:start
On the recommendation of someone
whose opinion I trust highly!

00:06:19.013 --> 00:06:20.681 position:33% line:89% align:start
My girl here.

00:06:20.815 --> 00:06:22.650 position:38% line:89% align:start
[laughs]

00:06:22.783 --> 00:06:25.052 position:38% line:89% align:start
[laughs]

00:06:25.186 --> 00:06:26.287 position:30% line:89% align:start
Yup, boyfriend!

00:06:26.419 --> 00:06:28.623 position:24% line:83% align:start
I keep telling you
that's not true!

00:06:30.524 --> 00:06:31.458 position:30% line:83% align:start
[NEWS ANCHOR 1]
Good night everyone

00:06:31.592 --> 00:06:33.794 position:13% line:89% align:start
and have a happy new year!

00:06:34.328 --> 00:06:35.663 position:41% line:89% align:start
[beeps]

00:06:35.796 --> 00:06:37.798 position:38% line:83% align:start
[SHIORI]
This year is almost over.

00:06:46.274 --> 00:06:49.476 position:10% line:83% align:start
It's not weird if I call him
on New Year's, right?

00:06:51.178 --> 00:06:52.613 position:13% line:83% align:start
[NEWS ANCHOR 2] We're back
covering one of the cities'

00:06:52.747 --> 00:06:54.048 position:19% line:89% align:start
biggest annual events.

00:06:54.181 --> 00:06:56.083 position:21% line:83% align:start
Once again, the hall
is full of excited fans.

00:06:56.217 --> 00:06:58.252 position:16% line:83% align:start
[SHINOZAKI] That's weird.
Who'd be calling this late?

00:06:58.386 --> 00:07:02.623 position:10% line:83% align:start
[REPORTER] What did you think
of the event? Is this live?

00:07:02.757 --> 00:07:04.292 position:35% line:83% align:start
[SHINOZAKI]
Is this happening right now?

00:07:04.424 --> 00:07:05.860 position:13% line:89% align:start
Senpai's really calling me?

00:07:05.993 --> 00:07:07.628 position:35% line:83% align:start
[HAYAKAWA]
Don't say that on TV!

00:07:07.762 --> 00:07:09.997 position:19% line:83% align:start
[SHINOZAKI] Of course,
I can't believe I forgot!

00:07:10.131 --> 00:07:13.267 position:16% line:83% align:start
We exchanged contact info
over Christmas!

00:07:13.401 --> 00:07:15.803 position:10% line:89% align:start
I am the luckiest man alive!

00:07:15.937 --> 00:07:18.639 position:35% line:83% align:start
-[ringing]
-Or wait. Gotta answer first.

00:07:18.773 --> 00:07:20.675 position:10% line:89% align:start
Yes, hi. Shinozaki speaking.

00:07:20.808 --> 00:07:23.010 position:5% line:89% align:start
 <i>Sorry I took so long to answer.</i>

00:07:23.144 --> 00:07:25.112 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>I'm at my parents'</i>
 <i>and it's been busy.</i>

00:07:25.246 --> 00:07:29.050 position:19% line:83% align:start
Oh, is everything okay?
I can call you back if need be.

00:07:29.183 --> 00:07:31.185 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>No, no, I can talk now!</i>

00:07:31.319 --> 00:07:32.687 position:30% line:89% align:start
So, what's up?

00:07:33.220 --> 00:07:36.157 position:10% line:83% align:start
I just wanted to call and say
thank you for everything you did

00:07:36.290 --> 00:07:37.591 position:30% line:89% align:start
this past year.

00:07:37.725 --> 00:07:39.894 position:24% line:89% align:start
Thank me, but why?

00:07:40.928 --> 00:07:42.129 position:38% line:89% align:start
 <i>Because!</i>

00:07:42.263 --> 00:07:45.366 position:16% line:83% align:start
You've made such amazing
improvements over the past year.

00:07:45.498 --> 00:07:47.535 position:5% line:89% align:start
It's been a joy to see you grow.

00:07:47.668 --> 00:07:50.204 position:21% line:83% align:start
You've even helped me
do better too.

00:07:50.338 --> 00:07:51.372 position:41% line:89% align:start
[sighs]

00:07:52.373 --> 00:07:54.542 position:24% line:83% align:start
[SHINOZAKI] Really?
I kinda felt like a nuisance

00:07:54.675 --> 00:07:56.043 position:24% line:89% align:start
more than anything.

00:07:56.177 --> 00:07:57.578 position:30% line:89% align:start
Don't you know?

00:07:57.712 --> 00:08:00.114 position:10% line:83% align:start
When your senpai calls you to
thank you for a job well done,

00:08:00.247 --> 00:08:03.017 position:21% line:83% align:start
then you can just say
"Go me!". Okay, now say it.

00:08:03.150 --> 00:08:06.520 position:16% line:83% align:start
Well, if that's the case
then I guess go me?

00:08:06.654 --> 00:08:08.923 position:33% line:83% align:start
That's right,
you take that compliment!

00:08:09.056 --> 00:08:12.460 position:5% line:83% align:start
Oh? Did I just sneak in one last
abuse of authority

00:08:12.593 --> 00:08:14.028 position:16% line:89% align:start
before the year was over?

00:08:14.161 --> 00:08:16.163 position:10% line:83% align:start
[SHINOZAKI] I hope she keeps
abusing her authority

00:08:16.297 --> 00:08:19.033 position:24% line:83% align:start
into the next year
and every year after!

00:08:19.567 --> 00:08:21.802 position:16% line:89% align:start
And hey, one last thing.

00:08:21.936 --> 00:08:25.740 position:10% line:83% align:start
Of all the kohais I could've
had, I'm glad I have you.

00:08:26.907 --> 00:08:29.143 position:19% line:89% align:start
Me too! But in reverse.

00:08:29.276 --> 00:08:30.578 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:08:31.512 --> 00:08:32.913 position:41% line:89% align:start
I, um.

00:08:33.481 --> 00:08:36.751 position:5% line:89% align:start
I'm glad I have you as a senpai.

00:08:37.318 --> 00:08:39.754 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>You're the only one</i>
 <i>I could ever want.</i>

00:08:40.287 --> 00:08:41.622 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh!

00:08:43.991 --> 00:08:45.459 position:35% line:83% align:start
[HAYAKAWA]
Anyway,

00:08:45.593 --> 00:08:47.661 position:7% line:83% align:start
I'm looking forward to another
year of working together!

00:08:47.795 --> 00:08:50.231 position:21% line:83% align:start
[SHIORI] Yeah, same.
Let's keep up the good work.

00:08:53.134 --> 00:08:54.503 position:38% line:89% align:start
[chimes]

00:08:54.635 --> 00:08:57.538 position:13% line:83% align:start
[AKINA] I sensed something.
You should go to the Hatsumode

00:08:57.671 --> 00:08:58.839 position:38% line:89% align:start
Manager?

00:08:59.508 --> 00:09:01.675 position:35% line:83% align:start
[SHINOZAKI]
It could be fun.

00:09:01.809 --> 00:09:04.678 position:35% line:83% align:start
Especially
if Senpai came along too.

00:09:04.812 --> 00:09:06.814 position:13% line:89% align:start
Maybe I should invite her.

00:09:06.947 --> 00:09:07.982 position:47% line:89% align:start
Uh!

00:09:08.115 --> 00:09:11.252 position:33% line:83% align:start
My little bro
has a girlfriend now?

00:09:12.720 --> 00:09:14.255 position:44% line:89% align:start
What?

00:09:14.388 --> 00:09:17.324 position:5% line:83% align:start
What could've possibly given you
that extremely wrong impression?

00:09:17.458 --> 00:09:20.861 position:10% line:83% align:start
Well, how else do you explain
that cute getup you've got on?

00:09:20.995 --> 00:09:23.697 position:19% line:83% align:start
Hey! It was a gift from
my senpai at work.

00:09:23.998 --> 00:09:26.133 position:21% line:89% align:start
Your senpai? At work?

00:09:26.267 --> 00:09:28.335 position:19% line:89% align:start
Um. What is happening?

00:09:29.336 --> 00:09:31.038 position:30% line:89% align:start
A lady senpai?

00:09:31.605 --> 00:09:33.908 position:21% line:89% align:start
Well, she is a woman.

00:09:34.041 --> 00:09:35.910 position:38% line:83% align:start
Hold on,
I know what you're thinking.

00:09:36.043 --> 00:09:37.678 position:7% line:89% align:start
It's not like that in any way!

00:09:37.812 --> 00:09:41.749 position:10% line:83% align:start
So it's true. At long last my
little brother's found a woman.

00:09:41.882 --> 00:09:43.818 position:35% line:83% align:start
[SHINOZAKI]
Are you even listening?

00:09:44.885 --> 00:09:46.720 position:19% line:83% align:start
[SHIORI] My Tiny Senpai
will be right back

00:09:46.854 --> 00:09:49.090 position:16% line:89% align:start
after this cat nap. Meow!

00:09:50.024 --> 00:09:53.127 position:19% line:83% align:start
Shinozaki invited me to
Hatsumode this year.

00:09:53.260 --> 00:09:55.830 position:13% line:83% align:start
I wonder what I should wear
to the shrine.

00:09:56.964 --> 00:09:59.967 position:7% line:83% align:start
