00:19:08.049 --> 00:19:09.117 position:47% line:89% align:start
Uh!

00:19:09.249 --> 00:19:10.317 position:41% line:89% align:start
[sighs]

00:19:10.450 --> 00:19:11.619 position:33% line:89% align:start
Just go home!

00:19:11.753 --> 00:19:13.253 position:7% line:89% align:start
A spring wedding would be nice,

00:19:13.387 --> 00:19:15.089 position:27% line:83% align:start
but I'd prefer it
if you eloped today.

00:19:15.222 --> 00:19:18.126 position:19% line:83% align:start
We're not toys for you
to play out your fantasies with!

00:19:18.258 --> 00:19:20.128 position:24% line:89% align:start
Matrimony Beam. Go!

00:19:20.260 --> 00:19:21.929 position:10% line:89% align:start
Stop it! That's not a thing!

00:19:22.063 --> 00:19:24.766 position:7% line:83% align:start
All right, you've had your fun.
Now knock it off.

00:19:24.899 --> 00:19:25.867 position:44% line:89% align:start
What?

00:19:26.000 --> 00:19:27.869 position:7% line:89% align:start
You should know better though.

00:19:28.002 --> 00:19:30.038 position:38% line:89% align:start
Who? Me?

00:19:30.170 --> 00:19:31.606 position:16% line:89% align:start
I'm sorry about all that.

00:19:31.739 --> 00:19:34.341 position:10% line:83% align:start
My sister can be really rude
when she's like this.

00:19:34.474 --> 00:19:35.810 position:19% line:89% align:start
Thanks, but it's fine.

00:19:35.943 --> 00:19:38.813 position:16% line:83% align:start
It's nice seeing how well
the two of you get along.

00:19:39.547 --> 00:19:41.214 position:13% line:89% align:start
Is that what it looks like?

00:19:41.348 --> 00:19:43.483 position:10% line:83% align:start
'Cause it doesn't always feel
like we do.

00:19:44.619 --> 00:19:46.921 position:24% line:83% align:start
We're usually both
into the same kinds of things

00:19:47.055 --> 00:19:49.557 position:13% line:83% align:start
and that caused a whole lot
of fights growing up.

00:19:49.691 --> 00:19:52.359 position:21% line:83% align:start
[SHIORI] They're both
into the same things?

00:19:54.294 --> 00:19:55.530 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:19:55.663 --> 00:19:58.099 position:10% line:89% align:start
Oh, I uh didn't realize that.

00:19:59.299 --> 00:20:03.004 position:10% line:83% align:start
So, when you say you're both
into the same kinds of things,

00:20:03.137 --> 00:20:04.471 position:30% line:89% align:start
that must mean.

00:20:06.206 --> 00:20:07.975 position:35% line:83% align:start
[SHINOZAKI]
Oh, um.

00:20:08.810 --> 00:20:10.178 position:35% line:89% align:start
[BOTH sigh]

00:20:10.310 --> 00:20:11.679 position:41% line:83% align:start
[BOTH]
Hey, you two!

00:20:11.813 --> 00:20:13.413 position:21% line:83% align:start
You're gonna pick me
to give the big speech

00:20:13.548 --> 00:20:14.749 position:30% line:83% align:start
or whatever at
the wedding, right?

00:20:14.882 --> 00:20:16.017 position:24% line:89% align:start
You should pick me!

00:20:16.150 --> 00:20:17.785 position:19% line:83% align:start
I'm the groom's sister,
so it should be me!

00:20:17.919 --> 00:20:19.587 position:33% line:83% align:start
I'm the groom
and the bride's boss.

00:20:19.721 --> 00:20:21.689 position:27% line:83% align:start
-It should be me!
-No, it's me!

00:20:21.823 --> 00:20:23.024 position:41% line:89% align:start
No, me!

00:20:23.157 --> 00:20:25.626 position:13% line:83% align:start
-Family trumps everything.
-That's so old-fashioned!

00:20:25.760 --> 00:20:27.061 position:38% line:83% align:start
[YUTAKA]
That speech is mine!

00:20:27.195 --> 00:20:28.629 position:41% line:83% align:start
[AKINA]
I very much disagree!

00:20:28.763 --> 00:20:30.397 position:10% line:83% align:start
[HAYAKAWA] Oh, that's great,
now there're two of them.

00:20:30.531 --> 00:20:32.499 position:27% line:83% align:start
-You two, decide!
-You two, decide!

00:20:34.502 --> 00:20:36.604 position:16% line:83% align:start
-What are we deciding on?
-What are we deciding on?

00:20:36.738 --> 00:20:38.005 position:41% line:89% align:start
[sighs]

00:20:38.639 --> 00:20:39.841 position:13% line:89% align:start
Now that I think about it,

00:20:39.974 --> 00:20:42.043 position:10% line:83% align:start
did Yutaka ever go that crazy
over you?

00:20:42.176 --> 00:20:43.144 position:47% line:89% align:start
Uh!

00:20:43.611 --> 00:20:45.780 position:16% line:83% align:start
Oh, I am in no way small
or cute enough for her

00:20:45.913 --> 00:20:48.750 position:24% line:83% align:start
to ever react to me
like she did with Katase.

00:20:49.717 --> 00:20:51.318 position:47% line:89% align:start
Oh!

00:20:52.186 --> 00:20:53.320 position:47% line:89% align:start
Hm!

00:20:54.155 --> 00:20:55.255 position:13% line:89% align:start
Well, I think you're small

00:20:55.388 --> 00:20:57.491 position:30% line:83% align:start
and cute enough
to go crazy over.

00:20:59.060 --> 00:21:00.561 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:21:04.132 --> 00:21:06.734 position:24% line:89% align:start
Manager, that's uh.

00:21:06.868 --> 00:21:09.302 position:7% line:83% align:start
I'm thinking we print Shiorin's
face on these cute plates

00:21:09.436 --> 00:21:11.172 position:24% line:83% align:start
and give them away
as wedding favors.

00:21:11.304 --> 00:21:12.740 position:38% line:83% align:start
[SHIORI]
I'm "Shiorin" now?

00:21:12.874 --> 00:21:14.041 position:35% line:83% align:start
[SHINOZAKI]
What about my face?

00:21:14.175 --> 00:21:15.209 position:27% line:89% align:start
You don't matter.

00:21:15.342 --> 00:21:16.677 position:35% line:83% align:start
[SHINOZAKI]
That's just mean!

00:21:16.811 --> 00:21:18.846 position:19% line:83% align:start
Why not let your guests
pick from a catalog?

00:21:18.980 --> 00:21:21.348 position:10% line:83% align:start
[SHINOZAKI] Could you please
stop putting ideas in her head?

00:21:21.481 --> 00:21:25.052 position:27% line:83% align:start
[HAYAKAWA] Urgh!
That's quite enough of that!

00:21:25.186 --> 00:21:26.654 position:41% line:83% align:start
[BOTH]
Okay, fine.

00:21:27.955 --> 00:21:29.190 position:38% line:89% align:start
Come on.

00:21:29.322 --> 00:21:31.358 position:10% line:83% align:start
How about we all go and enjoy
the shrine together now?

00:21:31.491 --> 00:21:32.860 position:35% line:83% align:start
[SHINOZAKI]
Sounds like a plan.

00:21:32.994 --> 00:21:34.361 position:16% line:83% align:start
I wonder what food stalls
they have.

00:21:34.494 --> 00:21:35.663 position:35% line:83% align:start
[HAYAKAWA]
No, thank you.

00:21:35.797 --> 00:21:37.231 position:41% line:83% align:start
[AKINA]
You wanna put cat ears on?

00:21:37.364 --> 00:21:39.000 position:35% line:83% align:start
[HAYAKAWA]
Absolutely not! I said no!

